## Spec-First Principle

The `.feature` file is the source of truth for every feature. Any code change — new feature, iteration, or bug fix — MUST start by updating the relevant `.feature` file. Never change code without updating the spec first.

**Note**: Gherkin specs are being introduced. New features should include a `.feature` file in `/features/{N}-{slug}/`.

