## Development Workflow

Use `/new-feature` to orchestrate the full feature lifecycle, or invoke individual phases:

- @plan — Discuss and refine a feature idea into an implementation plan
- @spec — Write a Gherkin `.feature` specification
- @implement — Build the feature from its spec (bottom-up: types → logic → UI)
- @test — Write tests mapped to Gherkin scenarios and run the full suite

